{"type": "article", "id": 12382, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13210, "name": "智能办公桌"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 2283, "name": "挂钩"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122511xPOW5CQERqhz6Ks3.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tInfinity C by Jung Dongsung\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这款台灯叫做 “无限 C”，来自韩国设计师 Jung Dongsung，这个充满未来感的灯具可以被“拗”成“0”或 “9” 等酷酷的造型，顶部的环形框架里面设置了一个 LED 灯，圆形的顶部可以化身触摸屏，展示天气，窗口小工具，或是和智能手机配合使用。颜色上，台灯有五种色系选择，而且对比色的使用凸显着设计细节上的用心。<a href=\"http://www.jungdongsung.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>进入设计师个人主页，可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102502haSzewTCrjB6RiWG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102503BM2YU1L85aO3xyK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021025037r6hIioKfb42PqcH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102504IBPx6y8JVCWnmrHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40586797\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102504PhX6B7DWK9TV1ILG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102504EZ4WSgMJlwdAx85j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t World's First Smart Standing Desk That Talks \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这台桌子号称是世界上第一台可以站立可以说话的智能书桌。它可以根据用户使用的姿势提供坐式和站立式两种形态，同时，桌面配有智能案板，记忆板，扬声器，USB接口等智能设备，可以像 Siri 一样听从指令而给出反应，也可以配合手机 App，为用户提供更多服务。目前这款桌子正在 Indiegogo 上面众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/ergo-world-s-first-smart-standing-desk-that-talks#/story\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140121LKSn1tRshp2cHgaQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140121Dr285sdwyfbeIUSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65806452\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102505egWahMP9u5Bc2XQV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102505cuU8MYB5rOKflyad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102506LWpExiCYvJA1jURX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102506FQY2gEqusHMK3RbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102506GfZE67inJYPhsL14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210250757ciJrThmFoRwLl3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210250709D5q86GpATzVawn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tGiant Cross-Stitch Furniture by Ellinor Ericsson \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>哥本哈根设计师 Ellinor Ericsson 耿耿于怀于北欧设计的极简，这种极简主义甚至被人诟病为乏味无趣。于是 Ellinor Ericsson 试图在简单的设计的基础上加入一些有趣的装饰，她试图把洛可可风格和北欧风格结合在一起，在简单的桦木椅子上编织上五彩的十字扣，结构和材料是北欧式的，而颜色和装饰形状是洛可可式的，让简单的设计也变得好玩儿一点。这里是<a href=\"http://www.ellinorericsson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102508qoDIRkzAmJ94Pa58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021025086mdyIRchOwtfbA4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102508JqlUAc6LkOarCdj4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102509794FzTMnJQSAKeDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102509E0rMN2fIxl38LtvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210251048bTGZUgDlB6p2NV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102510EJ2ofAjpsT9tXbNG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102511EpSCcdu2xU4hD7yY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tHook-It Series by Vered Venezia\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>以色列设计师 Vered Venezia 推出了一套自定义挂钩系列，她提供给你各式各样的零件，而用户可以根据自己的喜好排列出不同的挂件，有落地式衣架，小物件托盘，墙壁小架子等等。她的设计灵感来自小时候玩过的玩具，试图用这样的方式吸引人们发挥创造力，自己动手的激情。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/veredvenezia\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看她更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021025118f7J3bFqCgEh2dit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102512EIe4HFqNzn3baCVx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102512TlEWOdF5UsYM9KCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102513FmzjhCTnesPKRLV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021025131HtyFWozbfpLVJxd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140121PT4srkCmBpKogY7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102514jbBN96zYps1lMR5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tWhite Apollo Moc by Native \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自加拿大温哥华的鞋履品牌 Native 最近为其经典鞋款 Apollo Moc 推出白色款式。这款鞋子因为使用了特殊的材料，整个鞋身只有 6 盎司的重量，再加上使用超细的纤维材质，有非常优秀的透气本领，而且全鞋身没有缝合的痕迹，听起来有点适合处女座呀。鞋子售价 70 美元，这是<a href=\"http://www.kicksonfire.com/tag/native/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102514nzvUyoL8Z1HgGhDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94211823\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102514r5Q0pBwJjbnx36cU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00735294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102515idN6PTjkXCqfWuBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00146843\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102515uMKZAroj3CmHNcIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67467249\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102516Bj8LAv016e9khWud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102516NP3X8fJ6MSA4LQ2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tTaliesin 4 by Yamagiwa\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自日本的 Yamagiwa 公司推出了一款新的台灯，其设计原型是弗兰克•劳埃德•赖特为美国威斯康星州设计的塔里埃森剧院。在台灯里面，他们使用了赖特最喜欢的颜色红色作为台灯的主体方块颜色，红色的色块看上去非常迷人，三个灯箱都可以散发光芒，被方向板分散，柔和静谧，在各种背景下几乎都可以和环境融为一体。这是 <a href=\"http://www.yamagiwa.co.jp/global/\" target=\"_blank\">Yamagiwa 工作室的主页</a>，可以查看其更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140122YOxCBvhJTQlN0Pye.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78606357\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140122BOrwqbLhY4jkH85g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140123cS8bFmJjCd3ZUOVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79095355\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401240HBg5KYrbnFivW6k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140125iHP5bpJvmAVf8ZLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140125vsPNtZ9Yw6SmoWc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401267w3TRuEredhnZkql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}